'''write a python program to accept the price, quantity of a product and print the actual bill, discount and netbill.
Allow 15% discount if bill exceeds to 1000 otherwise, Allow 5% discount'''

price=eval(input("Enter product price:"))
qty=eval(input("Enter quantity of product:"))
bill=price*qty
if bill>=1000:
	discount=bill*15/100
else:
	discount=bill*5/100
net_bill=bill-discount
print("Your actual bill is",bill)
print("Your discount is",discount)
print("Your net bill is",net_bill)
'''__________OUTPUT_________
Enter product price:2000
Enter quantity of product:1
Your actual bill is 2000
Your discount is 300.0
Your net bill is 1700.0

[Program finished]'''
